Package org.dellroad.stuff.vaadin22.data

Vaadin data provider and related classes.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AsyncDataProvider.Loader<T>
    Callback interface for asynchronous loading of data for a AsyncDataProvider.
    AsyncDataProvider.LoadListener
    Listener interface for notifications about AsyncDataProvider asynchronous load attempts.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AsyncDataProvider<T>
    A ListDataProvider that supports asynchronous loading.
    EnumDataProvider<T extends Enum<T>>
    A simple data provider containing Enum values.
    MapPropertySet
    Straightforward implementation of PropertySet supporting property values stored in a Map.
    SessionInfo
    Holds information gathered from one VaadinSession.
    VaadinSessionDataProvider<T extends SessionInfo>
    A DataProvider that provides an object corresponding to each live VaadinSession.
